
  To build a macOS piapp.app packing.

  In principle the produced piapp.app is standalone and ready for execution and distribution.
 It should work with the X11/Motif version and also with the wxWidget version, but the wxWidget
 version should be prefered since it is straight over Cocoa.
 
  To build and run :
    macOS> cd <path>/ProjectPI/BuildMgr
    macOS> <build piapp>  # preferably the wxWidget version.
    macOS> cd macOS_app
    macOS> ./build
    macOS> open piapp.app

  To distribute, for example :
    macOS> zip -qr piapp.app.zip piapp.app
    macOS> <distribute piapp.app.zip>
  on a target machine :
    macOS> <get piapp.app.zip>
    macOS> unzip -q piapp.app.zip
    macOS> open piapp.app
    
